      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      interface  Event3AsyncDelegate<T1,T2,T3>
      An Event3AsyncDelegate implements Action3Async as well as Event3Delegate and is meant as a specification for implementations that delegate calls to the Action3Async interface asynchronously to all subscribers of the Event3Delegate interface.
      interface  Event3Delegate<T1,T2,T3>
      An Event3Delegate implements Action3 as well as Event3 and is meant as a specification for implementations that delegate calls to the Action3 interface to all subscribers of the Event3 interface.

      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  Event3AsyncAdapter<T1,T2,T3>
      The Event3AsyncAdapter is class that adapts an Event3Delegate to Event3AsyncDelegate so that the original delegates subscribers can be invoked asynchronously.
      class  Event3Caller<T1,T2,T3>
      The Event3Caller is a Event3Delegate implementation that allows event distribution to a single subscriber.
      class  Event3Distributor<T1,T2,T3>
      The Event3Distributor is a Event3Delegate implementation that allows event distribution to multiple subscribers.
